title: Naruto Jump v1.0 [PD]
description:
Jump from platform to platform, collect coins, dodge and defeat the enemies and play with different characters in this new game based on the world of jumping ninja naruto.

Unlock all kinds of awesome characters to play!
Jump to where to get and reach unimaginable heights in this endless game!
Controls smooth and precise!

Tilt to move left or right, tap the screen to jump.
COMING SOON: we are trying our best to bring more characters in future updates.
